  <brief_title>The Effect of a Very Low-residual Diet on the Preparation Before Capsule Endoscopy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hillel Yaffe Medical Center</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hillel Yaffe Medical Center</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the proposed study is to compare prospectively two methods of small bowel&#xD;
      preparation prior capsule endoscopy study, the effect on the cleanliness and the quality of&#xD;
      visualization after two protocols of preparation: a 12 hour fast only versus 24 hour of a&#xD;
      very low residual diet (ENSURE, Abbott Laboratories, Israel) + 12 hour fast.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
